# ── Rust ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Cargo build products outside the default /target (benchmarks, examples, etc)
**/target/
# Generated lockfiles for libraries get committed; for binaries either way
# works. This repo ships both a lib and a bin, so we keep Cargo.lock.
# Rustc/rustfmt incremental caches
**/*.rs.bk
# mdBook / rustdoc output
/book/

